Last-updated: 
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] Shared libs

- Place common functionality into internal shared libs (.la) instead of
  static inclusions (.a) all around
- use systemwide netcdf (instead of vtkNetCDF copy) and uuid libraries
- build of kvlAutoCrop is disabled

